<div class="about-card mx-auto px-5">
  <h1 class="display-4 question">What is <em>PomoTomo</em>?</h1>
  <p>Pomotomo is a timer for the <em>pomodoro method</em>.</p>

  <h1 class="display-4 question">What is the pomodoro method?</h1>
  <p>It is a method for productivity created by Mr. Francesco Cirillo.</p>

  <h1 class="display-4 question">Why should I use PomoTomo?</h1>
  <p>With <em>PomoTomo</em>, you can log in to save your sessions:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Track your finished pomodoro rounds each time.</li>
    <li>Keep your sound settings for your next session.</li>
    <li>Customize the duration of your pomodoro and break round!</li>
  </ul>

  <h1 class="display-4 question">How do I use this?</h1>
  <ol>
    <li>Choose a task you need to do.</li>
    <li>Start the pomodoro timer.</li>
    <li>Work on the task until the alarm goes off.</li>
    <li>Start your five minute break.</li>
    <li>Repeat!</li>
    <li>Every four rounds you can take a longer 15 minute break!</li>
  </ol>

